website_summaries.verdict: In addition to being available for a decent price, this high-protein dog food is made with ingredients that benefit your dog's overall health.
pros: Derives its 32% protein from quality chicken and egg ingredients that come from cage-free animals
Also contains antioxidants, glucosamine, and omega fatty acids for multi-system support
No wheat, soy, corn, or artificial colors/flavors
cons: May cause stomach upset until dogs adjust to it
Some dogs don't like it, but most that try it do

customer_reviews.title: Helps keep weight on our sensitive pup
customer_reviews.text: I’m so sad it took me so long to find this product. Our GSP struggled with being able to hold weight and had skin allergies. I chalked it up to him being allergic to something in food and tried all kinds of grain free, boutique foods. He did okay on some but his stool output was insane and he was skin and bones. Some gave him diarrhea. I’m not sure what made me try this but I’m SO GLAD I found it. Our GSP looks incredible. He is muscular and has filled out so nicely. His coat is nice, he has firm, small stools consistently and he hasn’t had one problem with his skin since starting this food.
customer_reviews.author: tori

customer_reviews.title: My Aussie high energy frisbee playing ball chasing dogs love this!

This is their first bag of food and they have had about half now. They are thriving and I am pleased! And, this brand had a top 5 on the dog food review website. Make sure you transition into the food as suggested with your old food. It’s easier on your dogs digestion. Buy it!!

product_meta.title: Diamond Naturals Extreme Athlete Real Meat Recipe High Protein Dry Dog Food With Real Cage Free Chicken Protein 40Lb
product_meta.description:
Made with ingredients of exceptional quality, Diamond Naturals provides complete, holistic nutrition for every pet. Each Diamond Naturals dry formula is enhanced with superfoods and guaranteed probiotics, for optimal nutrition and digestive support. Diamond Naturals Extreme Athlete Adult Dog Chicken & Rice Formula is specifically formulated with optimal levels of protein, fat and whole grain to fuel your hard-working dog.
